title: Large, private balcony with panoramic views
posting_body: ['The Durham features just the right blend of charm and the ideal location for your next home.', 'Our community offers a variety of spacious apartment homes ranging from one-bedroom to three-bedroom floor plans.', 'Residents enjoy breathtaking views from our balconies, generous closet space, quartz counters, plank flooring and much, much more!', 'The Durham is nestled in the suburb of Edina with easy access to several major highways.', '-24-Hour Fitness Center Furnished with Life Fitness Equipment', '-Brushed stainless kitchen faucet with pull-down sprayer', '-Whirlpool stainless steel appliance suite with French door refrigerator and backless range', '-Controlled Access to Building Towers', '-Walk in showers in select two and three bedroom apartments', '-Designer tile backsplash with elegant quartz countertops', '-Moen Align bathroom collection in a chrome finish for a modern look', '-The Cinema Offers Cozy Seating for Private Viewing Parties', '-Large, Glass-Enclosed Indoor Pool, Sauna and Steam Room Open Year Round', '-Engineered wood plank flooring throughout', '-Spacious, walk-in closets in select apartment homes', '-The Playroom with Toys and Child-Friendly Computers', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
